caption:
- Dropped off, picked up, dropped off.
- Met with Client A. I'm worried about the state of the project, and yet it turns out there's maybe not that much for me to do in the next couple of weeks? It's sort of a relief, and yet I don't quite belive it.
- Wrote a tool to run my rsqrt on the input from the pd carrier rfft sums, so that it is running on exactly the same input that the pd rsqrt runs on. It's indeed producing something totally different. (See picture.) I'm not completely convinced that something's not wrong with the tool or some other setup detail, though.
- Made dinner.

I felt like I did more than that today, but that's probably because reducing work to list items has a distorting effect.
